00:09:13.680 --> 00:09:14.360
Sure.

00:09:29.240 --> 00:09:30.160
Let's go, Yao.

00:09:31.120 --> 00:09:31.560
Let's go.

00:09:32.440 --> 00:09:33.520
Captain Luo.

00:09:34.440 --> 00:09:35.480
Good luck.

00:09:36.960 --> 00:09:38.400
Sure thing!

00:09:39.560 --> 00:09:41.640
This has been an extraordinary day.

00:09:43.160 --> 00:09:44.200
(What is she)

00:09:44.680 --> 00:09:45.920
