Du Hongyue has never trusted me.

00:10:07.760 --> 00:10:09.000
When it comes to you, he...

00:10:12.240 --> 00:10:12.880
Do you get it?

00:10:13.160 --> 00:10:15.400
Are you telling the truth?

00:10:17.920 --> 00:10:18.680
