00:10:20.920 --> 00:10:22.920
You know it all too well.

00:10:28.000 --> 00:10:29.240
Someday,

00:10:29.880 --> 00:10:31.640
if I

00:10:31.640 --> 00:10:34.560
become the chairman
of North City Chamber of Commerce,

00:10:34.720 --> 00:10:38.080
I will take our chamber of commerce

00:10:39.000 --> 00:10:40.240
to new heights.

00:10:42.360 --> 00:10:44.360
It belongs to me

00:10:44.920 --> 00:10:46.640
and you.

00:10:50.280 --> 00:10:51.720
As soon as

00:10:52.560 --> 00:10:54.040
I get rid of him.

00:10:58.800 --> 00:10:59.400
Here.

